      {
        "step_no": 6,
        "text": "Roast in the preheated oven for 10-12 minutes, until salmon reaches an internal temperature of 125–130°F (52–54°C) for medium (or longer to desired doneness) and asparagus is tender-crisp. Thicker fillets may need up to 14 minutes.",
